                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>Kingston Jamaica</placeName>\n                                        <date>Novr 29<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> 5611</date>.</p>\n                              <p>To <addressee>Revd I Leeser</addressee></p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Respected Friend</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Your kind favor<lb/> accompanied by the Box\n                                        containing the pair<lb/> of Lamps and Occidents came to hand\n                                        for<lb/> the which I am greatly obliged. The contents<lb/>\n                                        of your esteemed letter I regret to <sic>sa</sic> I\n                                        cannot<lb/> at present fully answer being much fatigued<lb/>\n                                        both mentally and bodily by illness in the fa-<lb/>mily. To\n                                        the dreadful state of the <placeName>Island</placeName><lb/>\n                                        you are by this time no stranger.<lb/> My mind is too much\n                                        disturbed to give the<lb/> due particulars several distant\n                                        members of<lb/> our family have been attacked proving<lb/>\n                                        fatal to a cousin and her husband. The others<lb/> are thank\n                                        Heaven on the recovery.<lb/> How truly tis proven, that\n                                        there is \"good in evil.<lb/> How many hearts have turned to\n                                        righteous-<lb/>ness, how many unmindful of their own<lb/>\n                                        mortality have now discovered the mere<lb/> worm in\n                                        themselves. I write not my friend as one<lb/> over\n                                        Righteous, far from it I know myself</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p36970j2r/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
